trans-unit.source: Represents a collision record resulting from a collision between forest trust records.
Gets the collision record from the underlying Active Directory Domain Services service.
A <xref href="System.String"></xref> containing the collision record resulting from a collision between forest trust records.
Gets the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType"></xref> value for the forest trust collision.
A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType"></xref> value indicating the collision type.
Gets the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DomainCollisionOptions"></xref> value for the forest trust collision.

A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DomainCollisionOptions"></xref> value that provides information about the collision when the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision.CollisionType"></xref> type is <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType"></xref>.
Gets the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameCollisionOptions"></xref> value for the forest trust collision.

A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameCollisionOptions"></xref> value that provides information about the collision when the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision.CollisionType"></xref> type is <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType"></xref>.
